hadiths[113]{hadithnumber,text}:
135,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs hadas karey uski Namaz qabool nahi hoti jab tak ke wo (dobaara) wuzu na kar le. hazre-maut ke aik shakhs ne puchha ke hadas hona kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (paakhaanaa ke maqam se nikalney waali) awaz wali ya be-aawaaz wali hawa.
136,mein (eik martaba ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath masjid ki chhat par chadhaa. to aap ne wuzu kya aur kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke meri ummat ke log wuzu ke nishanat ki wjah se qiyamat ke din safaid peshani aur safaid hath paon walon ki shakl mein bulaey jaengey. to tum mein se jo koi apni chamak badhaanaa chahta hai to wo badha ley (yani wuzu achi tarah karey).
137,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki ke aik shakhs hai jisey ye khayal hota hai ke Namaz mein koi cheez (yaanii hawa nikalti ( malum hui hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (namaz se) na phirey ya na mudey, jab tak awaz na suney ya bo na paaey."
138,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) soey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kharraatey leney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur kabhi ( rawi ne us tarah) kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) let gaey. phir kharraatey leney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey iske baad Namaz padhi. phir Sufiyan ne ham se dusri martaba yahi hadis bayan ki Amr se, unhon-ne Kureb se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se naql kya ke wo kehtey they ke (eik martaba ( maine apni khala ( Ummul-Momenin ( Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar raat guzari , to ( maine dekha ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko uthey . jab thodi raat baqi reh gaee. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uth kar aik latkey huey mishkeezey se halka sa wuzu kya. Amr iska halkaapan aur maamooli hona bayan kartey they aur aap khadey ho kar Namaz padhney lagey, to maine bhi isi tarah wuzu kya. jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. phir aa kar aap ke baain taraf khada ho gaya aur kabhi Sufiyan ne ( an (an) يساره ( ki bajaey ( an (an) شماله (ka lafz kaha ( matlab donon ka aik hi hai) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey pher liya aur apni dahini taraf kar liya. phir Namaz padhi jis qadr Allah ko manzoor tha. phir aap let gaey aur so gaey. yahan tak ke kharraaton ki awaz aaney lagi phir aap ki khidmat mein muazzan hazir hua aur us ne aapko Namaz ki itlaa di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske sath Namaz ke liye tashrif ley gaey. phir aap ne Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya. ( Sufiyan kehtey hain ke) ham ne Amr se kaha, kuchh log kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhen soti thin, dil nahi sota tha. Amr ne kaha maine Ubaid-bin-Umair se suna, wo kehtey they ke anbiya (Alaihissalam) ke khuwab bhi wahi hotey hain. phir ( Quran ki ye ( aayat padhi. ''main khuwab mein dekhta hun ke main tujhey zabah kar raha hoon.''"
139,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maidan Arafaat se wapas huey. jab ghaati mein pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) utar gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (pahley ( peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur khub achi tarah nahi kya. tab maine kaha, ya Rasulullah ! Namaz ka waqt ( aa gaya) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz , tumharey aagey hai (yani Muzdalfa chal kar padhengey ( jab Muzdalfa mein pahunchey to aap ne khub achi tarah wuzu kya, phir jamat khadi ki gaee, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maghrib ki Namaz padhi, phir har shakhs ne apne oont ko apni jagah bithlaayaa , phir isha ki jamat khadi ki gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur un donon namazon ke darmyan koi Namaz nahi padhi."
140,"(eik martaba ( unhon-ne (yani Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) wuzu kya to apna chehra dhoya (is tarah ke pahley) pani ke aik chullu kulli ki aur naak mein pani diya. phir pani ka aik aur chullu liya, phir usko is tarah kya (yani ( doosrey hath ko milaya . phir us se apna chehra dhoya. phir pani ka doosra chullu liya aur us se apna daahinaa hath dhoya. phir pani ka aik aur chullu lekar usse apna bayan hath dhoya. iske baad apne sar ka masah kya. phir pani ka chullu lekar daahiney paon par daala aur usey dhoya. phir doosrey chullu se apna paon dhoya. yani bayan paon iske baad kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah wuzu kartey huey dekha hai."
141,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tum mein se koi apni biwi se hambistari karey to kahey ( بسم الله اللهم جنبنا الشيطان وجنب الشيطان ما رزقتنا‏ ( ''Allah ke naam ke sath shuru karta hun. aey Allaah! hamein shaitan se bacha aur shaitan ko us cheez se door rakh jo to (is hambistari ke nateejey mein) hamein ata farmaaey.'' ye dua padhney ke baad (jimaa' karne se) miyaan-beewii ko jo aulad milegii usey shaitan nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakta.
142,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye) baitul-khala mein dakhil hotey to ye ( dua ( padhtey ( اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الخبث والخبائث (aey Allah ! main napak jinon aur napak jinniyon se teri panah mangta hun.
143,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baitul-khala mein tashrif ley gaey. maine (baitul-khalaa ke qareeb) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye wuzu ka pani rakh diya. (baahar nikal kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye kisne rakhaa? jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batlaya gaya to aap ne (mere liye dua ki aur) farmaya ( اللهم فقهه في الدين (aey Allah ! usko Deen ki samajh ata farmaaiyo .
144,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi baitul-khala mein jaey to qible ki taraf munh karey na uski taraf pusht karey ( balke) mashriq ki taraf munh kar lo ya maghrib ki taraf .
145,"log kehtey they ke jab qazaae-haajat ke liye baitho to na qible ki taraf munh karo na baitul-maqdis ki taraf (ye sun kar) Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aik din mein apne ghar ki chhat par chadhaa to maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke 2 enton par qazaae-haajat ke liye baithey hain. phir Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( waase' se) kaha ke shayad tum un logon mein se ho jo apni peeth ke bal Namaz padhtey hain. tab maine kaha Allah ki qism ! main nahi janta (ke aap ka matlab kya hai) Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se wo shakhs murad liya jo Namaz mein zameen se uncha na rahe, sajde mein zameen se chimat jaey."
146,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan raat mein manase ki taraf qazaae-haajat ke liye jaatiin aur manase aik khula maidan hai. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha kartey they ke apni beeviyon ko parda karaaiye. magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par amal nahi kya. aik roz raat ko isha ke waqt Sauda-binte-Zama (rz), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya jo daraaz qad aurat thin, ( bahar ( gaiin. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein awaz di (aur kaha ( ham ne tumhen pehchan liya aur unki khahish ye thi ke parda (ka hukm) nazil ho jaey. chunanche (iske baad) Allah ne parde (ka hukm ( nazil farma diya."
147,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni beeviyon se) farmaya ke tumhen qazaae-haajat ke liye bahar nikalney ki ijazat hai. Hisham kehtey hain ke haajat se murad pakhaney ke liye ( bahar ( jana hai.
148,"(eik din main apni behan aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke makan ki chhat par apni kisi zarurat se chadhaa , to mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaae-haajat kartey waqt qible ki taraf pusht aur Sham (Syria) ki taraf munh kiye huey nazar aaey."
149,"aik din mein apne ghar ki chhat par chadhaa , to mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 enton par) qazaae-haajat ke waqt) baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh kiye huey nazar aaey."
150,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye nikaltey to main aur aik ladka apne sath pani ka bartan le aatey they. matlab ye hai ke us pani se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tahaarat kya kartey they.
151,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaae-haajat ke liye nikaltey, main aur aik ladka donon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey jatey they aur hamarey sath pani ka aik bartan hota tha."
152,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baitul-khala mein jatey to main aur aik ladka pani ka bartan aur neza lekar chaltey they. pani se aap tahaarat kartey they, (doosri sanad se) nazar aur Shazaan ne us hadis ki Shoba se mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai. anza laathii ko kehtey hain jis par phalkaa laga hua ho."
153,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab tum mein se koi pani piey to bartan mein saans na ley aur jab baitul-khala mein jaey to apni sharmgah ko daahiney hath se na chhuey aur na daahiney hath se istinja kare."
154,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tum mein se koi peshab karey to uzu (ang) apne daahiney hath se na pakdey , na daahiney hath se tahaarat karey, na (pani peetey waqt) bartan mein saans ley."
155,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik martaba ( rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aadat mubaraka thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( chaltey waqt) idhar-udhar nahi dekha kartey they. to main bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey peechhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahunch gaya. (mujhey dekh kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey patthar dhoond do, taake main unse paakii hasil karun ya usi jaisa (koii lafz ( farmaya aur farmaya ke haddi aur gobar na lana . chunanche main apne daman mein patthar ( bhar kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu mein rakh diye aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se hat gaya, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( qazaae-haajat se) farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pattharon se istinja kya."
156,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye gaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya ke main teen patthar talash karke aap ke paas laaun . lekin mujhey 2 patthar miley. tesraa dhoondaa magar mil na saka. to maine khushk gauhar utha liya. usko lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne patthar (to ( ley liye ( magar ( gobar phenk diya aur farmaya ye khud napak hai. (aur ye hadis) Ibraaheem-bin-Yoosuf ne apne bap se bayan ki. unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se suna, unse Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya."
157,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu mein har uzu (ang) ko eik-eik martaba dhoya.
158,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu mein aaza (angon) ko do-do baar dhoya.
159,"unhon-ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhon-ne ( Humran se) pani ka bartan maanga (aur lekar pahley) apni hatheliyon par teen martaba pani daala phir unhein dhoya. iske baad apna daahinaa hath bartan mein daala aur) pani lekar ( kulli ki aur naak saaf ki, phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya aur kohniyon tak teen baar donon hath dhoey phir apne sar ka masah kya phir (pani lekar ( takhnon tak teen martaba apne donon paon dhoey. phir kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke jo shakhs meri tarah aisa wuzu karey, phir 2 rakaat padhey , jis main apne nafs se koi baat na kare. to iske pichhli gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
160,"jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kya to farmaya main tum ko aik hadis sunata hun, agar Quran paak ki aik aayat ( nazil ( na hoti to main ye hadis tumko na sunaataa. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke jab bhi koi shakhs achi tarah wuzu karta hai aur (Khuloos ke saath) Namaz padhta hai to iske aik Namaz se dusri Namaz ke padhney tak ke gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. Urwa kehtey hain wo aayat ye hai) إن الذين يكتمون ما أنزلنا من البينات‏ ( (jiska tarjama ye hai ke) jo log Allah ki us nazil ki hui hidayat ko chhipaatey hain jo usney logon ke liye apni kitab mein bayan ki hai. un par Allah ki laanat hai aur (doosrey ( laanat karne walon ki laanat hai."
161,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs wuzu karey usey chahiye ke naak saaf karey aur jo patthar se istinja karey usey chahiye ke taaq adad (yani aik ya teen ya panch hi) se kare.
162,Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ke jab tum se koi wuzu karey to usey chahiye ke apni naak main pani de ( phir ( usey saaf karey aur jo shakhs pattharon se istinja karey usey chahiye ke bejod ‌ (yani aik ya teen) se istinja karey ‌ aur jab tum se koi so kar uthey to wuzu ke pani main hath dalney se pahley usey dhoney. kyonki tum mein se koi nahi janta ke raat ko iska hath kahan raha hai.
163,"(eik martaba) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein ham se peechhey reh gaey. phir (thodi der baad) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko pa liya aur Asr ka waqt aa pahuncha tha. ham wuzu karne lagey aur (achchhii tarah paon dhoney ki bajaey jaldi mein) ham paon par masah karne lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ويل للأعقاب من النار ( '' eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai'' 2 martaba ya teen martaba farmaya,"
164,"unhon-ne wuzu ka pani mangwaya aur apne donon hathon par bartan se pani ( lekar ( dala. phir donon hathon ko teen baar dhoya. phir apna daahinaa hath wuzu karke pani mein dala. phir kulli ki, phir naak mein pani diya, phir naak saaf ki. phir teen baar apna munh dhoya aur kohniyon tak teen baar hath dhoey, phir apne sar ka masah kya. phir har aik paon teen baar dhoya. phir farmaya maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap mere us wuzu jaisa wuzu farmaya kartey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs mere us wuzu jaisa wuzu karey aur (huzoor qalb se) 2 rakaat padhey jis main apne dil se baatein na kare. to Allah Taala iske pichhley gunah maaf kar deta hai."
165,wo hamarey paas se guzrey aur log lautey se wuzu kar rahe they. aap ne kaha achi tarah wuzu karo kyonke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (khushk) eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai.
166,"aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! maine tumhen char aisey kaam kartey huey dekha hai jinhein tumharey sathiyon ko kartey huey nahi dekha. wo kehney lagey, aey ibne- juraij! wo kya hain? ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke maine tawaaf ke waqt aapko dekha ke 2 Yamani ruknon ke siwa kisi aur rukn ko aap nahi chhootey ho. (doosrey) maine aapko basti jootey pahney huey dekha aur (teesrey) maine dekha ke aap zard rang istemal kartey ho aur (chauthii baat) maine ye dekhi ke jab aap Makka mein they, log (zil-hijja ka ( chaand dekh kar labbaik pukarney lagtey hain. (aur) Haj ka ehram baandh letey hain aur aap aathwein taareekh tak ehram nahi baandhtey. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke (doosrey ( arkaan ko to main yun nahi chhootaa ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Yamani ruknon ke ilawa kisi aur rukn ko chhotey huey nahi dekha aur rahe jootey, to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey jootey pahney huey dekha ke jinke chamdey par baal nahi they aur aap unhein ko pahney pahney wuzu farmaya kartey they, to main bhi unhi ko pahannaa chahiye pasand karta hun aur zard rang ki baat ye hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zard rang rangtey huey dekha hai. to main bhi usi rang se rangna pasand karta hun aur ehram baandhney ka mamla ye hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt tak ehram baandhtey huey nahi dekha jab tak aap ki ontni aapko lekar na chal padtii."
167,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni (marhooma) sahibzadi (Zainab (rz)) ko ghusl dene ke waqt farmaya tha ke ghusl dahini taraf se do, aur wuzu waley parts se ghusl ki shuruaat karo."
168,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jootaa pahnney, kanghi karne, wuzu karne aur apne har kaam mein dahini taraf se kaam ki shuruaat karne ko pasand farmaya kartey they."
169,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke namaze-Asr ka waqt aa gaya, logon ne pani talash kya, jab unhein pani na mila, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (eik bartan mein) wuzu ke liye pani laya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein apna hath daal diya aur logon ko hukm diya ke usi ( bartan ( se wuzu karein. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine dekha aapki ungliyon ke nichey se pani (chashmey ki tarah) ubal raha tha. yahan tak ke (qaafley ke) aakhiri aadmi ne bhi wuzu kar liya."
170,"hamarey paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh baal (mubaarak) hain, jo hamein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ya Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar walon ki taraf se miley hain. (ye sun kar) Ubeda ne kaha ke agar mere paas un baalon mein se aik baal bhi ho to wo mere liye saari duniya aur uski har cheez se zyada azeez hai."
171,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa mein) jab sar ke baal mundwaaey to sabse pahley abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal liye they.
172,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab kutta tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein se ( kuchh ( pi ley to usko saat (7) martaba dho lo (to paak ho jaaeyga).
173,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ne aik kuttey ko dekha, jo piyaas ki wjah se geelii mitti kha raha tha. to us shakhs ne apna moza liya aur usse pani bhar kar pilaaney laga, yahan tak ke usko khub sairaab kar diya. Allah ne us shakhs ke us kaam ki qadr ki aur usey jannat mein dakhil kar diya."
174,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein kuttey masjid mein aatey jatey they lekin log un jaghon par pani nahi chhidaktey they.
175,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( kuttey ke shikar ke mutaalliq ( malum kya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab to apne sadhaaey huey kuttey ko chhodey aur wo shikar kar ley to, to us ( shikar ( ko kha aur agar wo kutta us shikar mein se khud ( kuchh ( kha ley to, to ( usko ( na khaaiyo. kyonke ab us ne shikar apne liye pakda hai. maine kaha ke kuchh baar mein (shikaar ke liye) apne kuttey chhorta hon, phir iske sath doosrey kuttey ko bhi paata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phir mat kha . kyonke tum ne ( بسم الله ( apne kuttey par padhi thi. doosrey kuttey par nahi padhi."
176,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banda us waqt tak Namaz hi mein rehta hai jab tak wo masjid mein Namaz ka intizar karta hai. taa-waqte-ke wo hadas na kare. aik ajamii aadmi ne puchha ke aey Abu-Hurera ! hadas kya cheez hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke hawa jo peechhey se khaarij ho. (jisey urf aam mein gooz maarna kehtey hain).
177,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (namaazii Namaz se) us waqt tak na phirey jab tak (hawa ke nikalne ki) awaz na sun ley ya uski bo na pa ley.
178,"mein aisa aadmi tha jis ko sailaan mazi ki shikayat thi, magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kartey huey mujhey sharm aai. to maine ibne-al-Aswad ko hukm diya, unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usmein wuzu karna farz hai. is riwayat ko Shoba ne bhi Aamash se riwayat kya."
179,"agar koi shakhs sohbat karey aur mani na nikley. farmaya ke wuzu karey jis tarah Namaz ke liye wuzu karta hai aur apne uzu (khaas ang) ko dho ley. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke (ye ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. ( Zaid-bin-Khalid kehtey hain ke) phir maine iske barey mein Ali , Zuber , Talha aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se malum kya. sab ne us shakhs ke barey mein yahi hukm diya."
180,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Ansari ko bulaya. wo aaey to unke sar se pani tapak raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, shayad ham ne tumhen jaldi mein daal diya. unhon-ne kaha, ji haan. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi jaldi (ka kaam ( aa padey aur tumhen inzal na hua ho to tum par wuzu hai (ghusl zaroori nahin)."
181,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Arfa se lautey, to (pahaad ki) ghaati ki taraf mud gaey, aur rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ki. Usama kehtey hain ke phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur) mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (aa'zaa) par pani dalney laga aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu farmatey rahe. maine kaha ya Rasulullah! aap ( ab ( Namaz padhengey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Namaz ka maqam tumharey samney (yani Muzdalfa mein) hai. wahan Namaz padhi jaeygi."
182,"wo aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. ( wahan (aap rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye tashrif le gaey (jab aap wapas aaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu shuru kya ( to Mughira-bin-Shoba aap ke) wuzu waley parts ( par pani dalney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu kar rahe they aap ne apne munh aur hathon ko dhoya, sar ka masah kya aur mozon par masah kya."
183,"unhon-ne aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi aur apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein guzari. (wo farmatey hain ke) mein takiya ke arz (yani goshe) ki taraf let gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki ahliya ne (ma'mool ke mutaabiq) takiye ki lambai par (sar rakh kar) aaraam farmaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sotey rahe aur jab aadhi raat ho gaee ya usse kuchh pahley ya uske kuchh baad aap bedaar huey aur apne hathon se apni neend ko door karne ke liye aankhen malney lagey. phir aap ne sura aale-imraan ki aakhiri das aayatein padhin, phir aik mishkeeze ke paas jo (chhat mein) latkaa hua tha aap khadey ho gaey aur usse wuzu kya, khub achi tarah, phir khade ho kar Namaz padhney lagey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain maine bhi khadey ho kar isi tarah kya, jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya tha. phir ja kar mein bhi aap ke pahluey Mubarak mein khada ho gaya. aap ne apna daahinaa hath mere sar par rakha aur mera dayan kaan pakad kar usey modney lagey. phir aap ne 2 rakatein padhin. iske baad phir 2 rakatein padhin. phir 2 rakatein padhin. phir 2 rakatein , phir 2 rakatein, phir 2 rakatein padh kar iske baad aap ne witr padha aur let gaey, phir jab muazzan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, to aap ne uth kar do rakaat maamooli ( taur par) padhein . phir bahar tashrif la kar subah ki Namaz padhi."
184,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aisey waqt aai jabke suraj ko gehen lag raha tha aur log khadey ho kar Namaz padh rahe they, kya dekhti hon wo bhi khadey ho kar Namaz padh rahi hain. maine kaha ke logon ko kya ho gaya hai? to unhon-ne apne hath se aasman ki taraf ishara karke kaha, Subhan-Allah ! maine kaha (kya ye ( koi ( khas ( nishani hai? to unhon-ne ishaarey se kaha ke haan. to main bhi aap ke sath Namaz ke liye khadi ho gaee. (aap ne itna farmaya ke) mujh par ghashii taarii honey lagi aur main apne sar par pani dalney lagi jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to aap ne Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki aur farmaya, aaj koi cheez aisi nahi rahi jis ko maine apni usi jagah na dekh liya ho yahan tak ke jannat aur dozakh ko bhi dekh liya aur mujh par ye wahi ki gaee hai ke tum logon ko qabron mein aazmaya jaeyga dajjal jaisi aazmaish ya iske qareeb qareeb .) rawi ka bayan hai ke) mein nahi janti ke Asma ne kon sa lafz kaha, tum mein se har aik ke paas ( Allah ke Farishtey ( bhejey jaeinge aur us se kaha jaeyga ke tumhara us shakhs (yani Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke barey mein kya khayal hai? phir Asma ne lafz emaandaar kaha ya yaqin rakhney wala kaha, mujhey yad nahi. (bahar-haal wo shakhs) kahega ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain. wo hamarey paas nishaniyan aur hidayat ki roshni lekar aaey. ham ne (usey) qabool kya, eman laaey, aur (aap ka ( ittaba (pairvi) kya. phir (is se) keh diya jaeyga to so ja dar-haaleike to mard Saleh hai aur ham jantey they ke to momin hai. aur bahar-haal munafiq ya shakki aadmi , Asma ne kon sa lafz kaha mujhey yad nahi. (jab us se puchha jaaeyga) kahega ke main ( kuchh ( nahi janta, maine logon ko jo kehtey suna, wahi maine bhi keh diya."
185,"kya aap mujhey dikhaa saktey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kis tarah wuzu kya hai? Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan! phir unhon-ne pani ka bartan mangwaya pahley pani apne hathon par daala aur 2 martaba hath dhoey. phir teen martaba kulli ki, teen baar naak saaf ki, phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya. phir kohniyon tak apne donon hath 2-2 martaba dhoey. phir apne donon hathon se apne sar ka masah kya. us taur par apne hath (pahley ( aagey laey phir peechhey ley gaey. ( masah ( sar ke shuruati hissey se shuru kya. phir donon hath guddi tak ley ja kar wahin wapas laey jahan se ( masah ( shuru kya tha, phir apne pair dhoey."
186,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne pani ka tasht mangwaya aur un (poochhney waalon) ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sa wuzu kya. (pahley tasht se) apne hathon par pani giraayaa. phir teen baar hath dhoey, phir apna hath tasht mein daala (aur pani liyaa) phir kulli ki, naak mein pani daalaa, naak saaf ki, teen chulluon se, phir apna hath tasht mein daala aur teen martaba munh dhoya. phir apne donon hath kohniyon tak 2 baar dhoey. phir apna hath tasht mein daala aur sar ka masah kya. ( pahley) aagey laey phir peechhey ley gaey, aik baar. phir takhnon tak apne donon paon dhoey."
187,"(eik din) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas do-pahar ke waqt tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye wuzu ka pani hazir kya gaya jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu farmaya, log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ka bacha hua pani lekar usey (apne badan par) pherney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki 2 rakatein ada kiin aur Asr ki bhi 2 rakatein aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (aad ke liye) aik neza tha."
188,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik piyala mangwaya . jis mein pani tha. us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath dhoey aur usi piyaale mein munh dhoya aur is mein kulli farmai, phir farmaya, to tum log usko pi lo aur apne chehron aur seenon par daal lo."
189,"Mehmood wahi hain ke jab wo chhotey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un hi ke kuwein (ke pani ( se unke munh mein kulli dali thi aur Urwa ne usi hadis ko Miswar wghaira se bhi riwayat kya hai aur har aik ( rawi ( un donon mein se aik doosrey ki tasdeeq kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu farmatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bachey huey wuzu ke pani par sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) jhagadney ke qareeb ho jatey they."
190,"meri khala mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gain aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! mera ye bhanja bimar hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sar par apna hath phera aur mere liye barkat ki dua farmai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ka bacha hua pani piyaa. phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kamar ke peechhey khada ho gaya aur maine mohre-nubuwat dekhi jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke moondhon ke beech aisi thi jaisey chhapparkhat ki ghundii. (ya kabootar ka andaa)."
191,"( wuzu kartey waqt) unhon-ne bartan se (pahley ( apne donon hathon par pani dala. phir unhein dhoya. phir dhoya. (ya yun kaha ke) kulli ki aur naak mein aik chullu pani daala aur teen martaba isi tarah kya. phir teen martaba apna chehra dhoya phir kohniyon tak apne donon hath 2-2 baar dhoey. phir sar ka masah kya. agli taraf aur pichhli taraf ka aur takhnon tak apne donon paon dhoey, phir kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wuzu isi tarah hua karta tha."
192,"meri maujoodgii mein Amr bin Hasan ne Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke barey mein poochha. to Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani ka aik tasht mangwaya , phir un ( logon (ke dikhaaney ke liye wuzu ( shuru ( kya. (pahley ( tasht se apne hathon par pani giraayaa. phir unhein teen baar dhoya. phir apna hath bartan ke andar daala , phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani daal kar naak saaf ki, teen chulluon se teen baar . phir apna hath bartan ke andar daala aur apne munh ko teen baar dhoya. phir apna hath bartan ke andar daala aur donon hath kohniyon tak 2-2 baar dhoey ( phir ( sar par masah kya is tarah ke (pahley ( aagey ki taraf apna hath laey phir peechhey ki taraf ley gaey. phir bartan mein apna hath daala aur apne donon paon dhoey (doosri riwayat mein) ham se Musa ne, unse Wuhaib ne bayan kya ke aap ne sar ka masah aik baar kya."
193,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aurat aur mard sab aik sath (eik hi bartan se) wuzu kya kartey they. (yani wo mard aur auratein jo aik doosrey ke mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) hotey ( .
194,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif laey. mein bimar tha aisa ke mujhey hosh tak nahi tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur apne wuzu ka pani mujh par chhidkaa , to mujhey hosh aa gaya. maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! mera waaris kon hoga? mera to sirf aik kalaala waaris hai. is par aayat meeraas nazil hui."
195,"(eik martaba ( Namaz ka waqt aa gaya, to jis shakhs ka makan qareeb hi tha wo wuzu karne apne ghar chala gaya aur kuchh log ( jinke makan door they) reh gaey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas patthar ka aik lagan laya gaya. jis mein kuchh pani tha aur wo itna chhota tha ke aap usmein apni hatheli nahi phaila saktey they. ( magar ( sab ne us bartan ke pani se wuzu kar liya, ham ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke tum kitney log they? kaha usi ( 80 ( se kuchh zyada hi they."
196,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik piyala mangaya jis mein pani tha. phir usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon aur chehrey ko dhoya aur usi mein kulli ki.
197,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( hamarey ghar ( tashrif laaey, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye taanbey ke bartan mein pani nikala . (is se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya. teen baar chehra dhoya , 2-2 baar hath dhoey aur sar ka masah kya. (is tarah ke) pahley aagey ki taraf ( hath ( laey. phir peechhey ki taraf le gaey aur pair dhoey."
198,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari zyada ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni (doosri ( beeviyon se is baat ki ijazat lelii ke aapki teemaardaarii mere hi ghar ki jaey. unhon-ne aapko ijazat de di, (eik roz) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan (sahaaraa lekar ( ghar se nikley. aap ke paon (kamzorii ki wjah se) zameen par ghisat'tey jatey they, Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik aadmi ke darmyan (aap baahar) nikley they. Ubaidullah (hadees k raawii) kehte hain ke maine ye hadis Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunai, to wo boley, tum jaante ho doosra aadmi kon tha, maine arz kya ke nahi. kehney lagey wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati thin ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar mein dakhil huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka marz badh gaya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere uper aisi saat (7) mushkon ka pani dalo , jinke munh na kholey gaey hun. taake main (sukoon ke baad) logon ko kuchh wasiiyat karun. (chunaanche) aapko Hafsa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki (doosri ( biwi ke lagan mein (jo taanbe ka tha) betha diya gaya aur hamne aap par un mushkon se pani bahana shuru kya. jab aap ham ko ishara farmaney lagey ke bas ab tum ne apna kaam pura kar diya to iske baad aap logon ke paas bahar tashrif ley gaey."
199,"mere chacha bahut zyada wuzu kya kartey they (ya ye ke wuzu mein bahut pani bahaatey they) aik din unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke mujhey batlaaiye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis tarah wuzu kya kartey they. unhon-ne pani ka aik tasht mangwaya . usko (pahley ( apne hathon par jhukaya . phir donon hath teen baar dhoey. phir apna hath tasht mein daal kar) pani liya aur) aik chullu kulli ki aur teen martaba naak saaf ki. phir apne hathon se aik chullu (pani) liya aur teen baar apna chehra dhoya. phir kohniyon tak apne donon hath 2-2 baar dhoey. phir hath mein pani lekar apne sar ka masah kya. to (pahley apne hath ( peechhey le gaey, phir aagey ki taraf laey. phir apne donon paon dhoey aur farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah wuzu kartey dekha hai."
200,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani ka aik bartan talab farmaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik chaudey munh ka piyala laya gaya jis mein kuchh thoda pani tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungliyan usmein daal dein. Anas kehtey hain ke main pani ki taraf dekhney laga. pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phoot raha tha. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke us (eik piyaale) pani se jin logon ne wuzu kya, wo 70 (70) se assii (80) tak they."
201,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab dhotey ya (ye kaha ke) jab nahatey to aik saa se lekar panch mudd tak (paanii istemal farmatey they) aur jab wuzu farmatey to aik mudd (paanii) se.
202,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mozon par masah kya. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne walid maajid umr (Raziallahu anhu) se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha ( sach hai aur yad rakho ( jab tum se Sad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi hadis bayan farmaaein, to iske mutaalliq unke siwa ( kisi) doosrey aadmi se mat poochho aur Musa-bin-Aqba kehtey hain ke mujhey abu-Nazar ne batlaya , unhein abu-Salma ne khabar di ke Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne unse ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye ( hadis bayan ki. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne betey ( Abdullah se aisa kaha,"
203,"(eik dafa'a) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye bahar gaey to Mughira pani ka aik bartan lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey gaey, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaae-haajat se farigh ho gaey to Mughira ne (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wuzu karatey huey) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke aaza mubaarka) par pani dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur mozon par masah farmaya,"
204,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mozon par masah kartey huey dekha. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) mein Harab aur Aban ne Yahya se hadis naql ki hai.
205,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne amaamey aur mozon par masah kartey dekha. usko riwayat kya Mamar ne Yahya se, wo abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Amr se naqal ki aur kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha (aap waqei aisa hi kya kartey they)."
206,"mein aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, to maine chaha (ke wuzu kartey waqt) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mozey utaar daalun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein rehney do. chunkey jab maine unhein pehna tha to mere paon paak they. (yani mein wuzu se tha) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un par masah kya."
207,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bakri ka shana khaayaa. phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya.
208,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakri ke shaane se kaat-kaat kar kha rahe they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye bulaey gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhuri daal di aur Namaz padhi, nayaa wuzu nahi kya."
209,"fateh khaibar waley saal wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sahbaa ki taraf, jo khaibar ke qareeb aik jagah hai pahunchey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz padhi, phir naashta mangwaya gaya to siwaey sattu ke aur kuchh nahi laya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya to wo bhigo diye gaey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaya aur ham ne ( bhi) khaayaa. phir maghrib (ki Namaz (ke liye khadey ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kulli ki aur ham ne ( bhi) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur nayaa wuzu nahi kya."
210,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke yahan ( bakri ka ( shana khaya phir Namaz padhi aur nayaa wuzu nahi farmaya,"
211,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh piyaa, phir kulli ki aur farmaya ismein chiknai hoti hai. us hadis mein Aqeel ki Yunus aur Saleh bin kaisaan ne Zohri se naqal ki hai."
212,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz padhtey waqt tum mein se kisi ko oongh aa jaey, to chahiye ke wo so rahe yahan tak ke neend (ka asar ( usse khatm ho jaey. isliye ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz padhney lagey aur wo oongh raha ho to wo kuchh nahi janey ga ke wo ( Allah Taala se) maghfirat talab kar raha hai ya apne nafs ko baddua de raha hai."
213,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum Namaz mein oonghney lago to so jana chahiye phir us waqt Namaz padhey jab jaan ley ke wo kya padh raha hai.
214,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har Namaz ke liye nayaa wuzu farmaya kartey they. maine kaha tum log kis tarah kartey they, kehney lagey ham mein se har aik ko iska wuzu us waqt tak kafi hota, jab tak koi wuzu todney wali cheez pesh na aa jati. (yani peshaab, paakhaanaa, ya neend wghaira)."
215,"ham khaibar waley saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jab Sehbaa mein pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Asr ki Namaz padhai. jab Namaz padh chukey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaane mangwaaey. magar (khaane mein) sirf sattu hi laya gaya. so ham ne (usi ko) khaya aur piyaa. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kulli ki, phir hamein maghrib ki Namaz padhai aur) nayaa) wuzu nahi kya."
216,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik baar Madina ya makke ke aik baagh mein tashrif ley gaey. ( wahan (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 shakhson ki awaz suni jinhein unki qabron mein azab kya ja raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un par azab ho raha hai aur kisi bahut badey gunah ki wjah se nahi phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya baat ye hai ke aik shakhs unmein se peshab ke chheenton se bchney ka ehtimaam nahi karta tha aur doosra shakhs chughal khorii kya karta tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (khajoor ki) aik dali mangwai aur usko tod kar do tukdey kye aur unmein se (eik-eik tukdaa) har aik ki qabr par rakh diya. logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kyon kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya isliye ke jab tak ye daaliyaan khushk hon shayad us waqt tak un par azab kam ho jaey.
217,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye bahar tashrif le jatey to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pani laataa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se istinja farmatey.
218,"(eik martaba ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 qabron par guzrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un donon qabr walon ko azab diya ja raha hai aur kisi badey gunah par nahi. aik to unmein se peshab se ehtiyat nahi karta tha aur doosra chughal khorii kya karta tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik harii tahnii lekar beech se iske 2 tukdey kiye aur har aik qabr par aik tukda gaad diya. logon ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (aisa) kyon kiya? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, shayad jab tak ye tahniyaan khushk na hon un par azab mein kuchh kami rahe. ibne-musanna ne kaha ke us hadis ko ham se Wakee ne bayan kya, unse Aamash ne, unhon-ne Mujahid se isi tarah suna."
219,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dehati ko masjid mein peshab kartey huey dekha to logon se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usey chhod do jab wo farigh ho gaya to pani mangaa kar aap ne (is jagah) baha diya.
220,"aik dehati khada ho kar masjid mein peshab karne laga. to log is par jhapatney lagey. (ye dekh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya ke usey chhod do aur uske peshab par pani ka bharaa hua dol ya kuchh kam bharaa hua dol baha do. kyonke tum narmii ke liye bhejey gaey ho, sakhti ke liye nahi."
221,aik dehati shakhs aaya aur us ne masjid ke aik koney mein peshab kar diya. logon ne usko mana kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein rok diya. jab wo peshab karke farigh hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (ke peshab ( par aik dol pani bahaney ka hukm diya. chunanche baha diya gaya.
222,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik bachcha laya gaya. usne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey par peshab kar diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangaya aur is par daal diyaa.
223,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmate-aqdas mein apna chhota bachcha lekar aaiin. jo khana nahi khata tha. (yani doodh peeta tha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey apni god mein bitha liya. us bachchey ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey par peshab kar diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangaa kar kapdey par chhidak diya aur usey nahi dhoya.
224,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi qaum ki koodi par tashrif laey ( to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan khadey hokar peshab kya. phir pani mangaayaa. mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pani lekar aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu farmaya.
225,(eik martaba ( main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ja rahe they ke aik qaum ki koodi par (jo ( aik diwar ke peechhey ( thi) pahunchey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah khadey ho gaey jis tarah ham tum mein se koi (shakhs) khada hota hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peshab kya aur main aik taraf hat gaya. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ishara kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (parde ki gharaz se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki eidiyon ke qareeb khada ho gaya. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peshab se farigh ho gaey. (b-waqt zarurat aisa bhi kya ja sakta hai.)
226,abu-Musa Ash-ari peshab (ke baare) mein sakhti se kaam letey they aur kehtey they ke Bani-Israeel mein jab kisi ke kapdey ko peshab lag jata. to usey kaat daaltey. abu-Huzaifa kehtey hain ke kash! wo apne us tashaddud se ruk jatey (kyonke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi qaum ki koodi par tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan khadey ho kar peshab kya.
227,"aik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! farmaiye ham mein se kisi aurat ko kapdey mein haiz aa jaey (to ( wo kya karey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke pahley) usey khurchey, phir pani se ragdey aur pani se dho daley aur usi kapdey mein Namaz padh ley."
228,"abu-Habeesh ki beti Fatima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur us ne kaha ke main aik aisi aurat hon jisey istihaza ki bimari hai. isliye main paak nahi rehti to kya main Namaz chhod dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi, ye aik rag (ka khoon ( hai haiz nahi hai. to jab tujhey haiz aaey to Namaz chhod de aur jab ye din guzar jayen to apne ( badan aur kapdey ( se khoon ko dho daal phir Namaz padh . Hisham kehtey hain ke mere bap Urwa ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye ( bhi) farmaya ke phir har Namaz ke liye wuzu kar yahan tak ke wahi ( haiz ka ( waqt phir aa jaey."
229,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se janabat ko dhoti thi. phir (usko pahan kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif ley jatey aur pani ke dhabbey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey mein hotey they.
230,maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se us mani ke baare mein puchha jo kapdey ko lag jaey. to unhon-ne farmaya ke main mani ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se dho dalti thi phir aap Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif le jatey aur dhoney ka nishan (yaani) pani ke dhabbe Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey mein baqi hotey.
231,"maine us kapdey ke mutaalliq jis mein janabat ( napaki (ka asar aa gaya ho, Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se suna wo kehtey they ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se mani ko dho dalti thi phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye bahar nikaltey aur dhoney ka nishan yani pani ke dhabbey kapdey mein hotey."
232,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se mani ko dho dalti thin (wo farmati hain ke) phir (kabhii) mein aik dhabba ya kai dhabbey dekhti thi.
233,kuchh log ukul ya Uraina ( qabeelon (ke Madina mein aaey aur bimar ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Liqaah mein janey ka hukm diya aur farmaya ke wahan oonton ka doodh aur peshab piein. chunanche wo Liqah chaley gaey aur jab achchhey ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ko qatl karke wo janwaron ko haank kar ley gaey. subah-subah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (is waaqie ki) khabar aai. to aap ne unke peechhey aadmi daudaaey . din chadhey wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pakad kar laey gaey. aap ke hukm ke mutabiq unke hath paon kaat diye gaey aur aankhon mein garm salaakhein pher di gain aur (Madina ki) pathreeli zameen mein daal diye gaey. ( piyaas ki shiddat se) wo pani maangtey they magar unhein pani nahi diya jata tha. abu-Qilaba ne (unke jurm ki sangeeni zahir kartey huey) kaha ke un logon ne chori ki aur charwaahon ko qatl kya aur (aakhir) eman se phir gaey aur Allah aur uske rasool se jang ki.
234,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid ki tameer se pahley Namaz bakriyon ke baadey mein padh liya kartey they. ( malum hua ke bakriyon wghaira ke baadey mein b-waqt zarurat Namaz padhi ja sakti hai).
235,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se choohey ke baare mein puchha gaya jo ghi mein gir gaya tha. farmaya usko nikal 2 aur uske aas-paas (ke ghi ( ko nikal pheinko aur apna ( baqi ( ghi istemal karo.
236,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se choohey ke barey mein malum kya gaya jo ghi mein gir gaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us choohey ko aur uske aas-paas ke ghi ko nikal kar phenk do. Ma'n (معن) kehtey hain ke Malik ne itni baar ke main gin nahi sakta (ye hadis) Ibne-Abbas se aur unhon-ne Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki hai.
237,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya har zakhm jo Allah ki raah mein musalman ko lagey wo qiyamat ke din usi haalat mein hoga jis tarah wo laga tha. usmein se khoon bahtaa hoga. jiska rang (to ( khoon ka sa hoga aur khushbu mashk ki si hogi.
238,ham (log) duniya mein pichhley zamaney mein aaey hain (magar aakhirat mein) sabse aagey hain.
239,(ye bhi) farmaya ke tum mein se koi thahrey huey pani mein jo jari na ho peshab na kare. phir usi mein ghusl karne lagey?
240,"aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba sharif mein sajde mein they. (eik dusri sanad se) ham se Ahmed bin Usman ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shureh-bin-Muslima ne, kaha ham se Ibrahim bin-Yoosuf ne apne bap ke waastey se bayan kya, wo Abu-Ishaq se riwayat kartey hain. unse Amr-bin-Memoon ne bayan kya ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse hadis bayan ki ke aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke nazdeek Namaz padh rahe they aur abu-Jahal aur uske sathi ( bhi wahin ( baithey huey they, to unmein se aik ne doosrey se kaha ke tum mein se koi shakhs hai jo qabeeley ki (jo ( ontni zabah hui hai) uski ( ojhdii utha laey aur) la kar) jab Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein jayen to unki peeth par rakh de. ye sun kar unmein se aik sabse zyada bad-bakht (aadmi) utha aur wo ojhdii lekar aaya aur dekhta raha jab aap ne sajda kya to usne us ojhdii ko aap ke donon kandhon ke darmyan rakh diya (Aabdullaah-bin-Mas'ood kehtey hain) mein ye (sab kuchh) dekh raha tha magar kuchh na kar sakta tha. kash! (is waqt) mujhey rokney ki taqat hoti. Abdullah kehtey hain ke wo hansney lagey aur (hansii ke maarey) lot-pot honey lagey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein they (bojh ki wjah se) apna sar nahi utha saktey they. yahan tak ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aaein aur wo bojh aap ki peeth se utaar kar phainkaa, tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar uthaya phir teen baar farmaya, ya Allaah! to Quraish ko pakad le, ye ( baat ( un kaafiron par bahut bhari hui ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein baddua di. Abdullah kehtey hain ke wo samajhtey they ke us Shahar (Makka) mein jo dua ki jaey wo zaroor qabool hoti hai phir aap ne ( unmein se) har aik ka ( juda judaa ( naam liya ke aey Allah ! un zaalimon ko zaroor halaak kar de. abu-Jahal, Utba-bin-Rabeea, Sheba bin Rabee , Waleed bin Utba, Umayya bin-Khalaf aur Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet ko. saatwein (aadmi) ka naam (bhi) liya magar mujhey yad nahi raha. us zaat ki qism jiske qabzey mein meri jaan hai ke jin logon ke (badduaa kartey waqt) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne naam liye they, maine unki (laashon) ko badr ke kuwein mein padaa hua dekha."
241,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik martaba) apne kapdey mein thookaa. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) ne farmaya ke Saeed-bin-abii-Maryam ne us hadis ko tawaalat ke sath bayan kya unhon-ne kaha ham ko khabar di Yahya bin Ayub ne, kaha mujh se Humaid ne bayan kya, kaha maine Anas se suna, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain."
242,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke peeney ki har wo cheez jo nasha laney wali ho haram hai.
243,"logon ne unse poochha, aur (main us waqt Sehal ke itna qareeb tha ke) mere aur unke darmyan koi doosra rukawat na tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (uhud ke) zakhm ka ilaaj kis dawaa se kya gaya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke is baat ka jaanney wala ( ab ( mujh se zyada koi nahi raha. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apni dhaal mein pani latey aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh se khoon dhoteen phir aik boriye ka tukda jalaayaa gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhm mein bhar diya gaya."
244,mein (eik martaba) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aapko apne hath se miswak kartey huey paya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh se Aa-Aa ki awaz nikal rahi thi aur miswak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh mein thi jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qai kar rahe hun.
245,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to apne munh ko miswak se saaf kartey.
246,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine dekha ke) khuwab mein) miswak kar raha hun to mere paas 2 aadmi aaey. aik unmein se doosrey se bada tha, to maine chhotey ko miswak de di phir mujh se kaha gaya ke badey ko do. tab maine unmein se badey ko di. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke us hadis ko Naeem ne ibne-Mubarak se, wo Usama se, wo Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se mukhtasar taur par riwayat kya hai."
247,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum apne bistar par letney aao to is tarah wuzu karo jis tarah Namaz ke liye kartey ho. phir dahini karwat par let kar yun kaho (اللهم أسلمت وجهي إليك ، Mina padhi. وفوضت أمري إليك ، Mina padhi. وألجأت ظهري إليك ، Mina padhi. رغبة ورهبة إليك ، Mina padhi. لا ملجأ wla منجا منك إلا إليك ، Mina padhi. اللهم آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت ، Mina padhi. وبنبيك الذي أرسلت‏ ) ''aey Allah ! maine apna chehra teri taraf jhukaa diya. apna mamla terey hi sipurd kar diya. maine terey sawab ki tawaqqo aur terey azab ke dar se tujhey hi pusht-panaah bana liya. terey siwa kahin panah aur nijat ki jagah nahi. aey Allaah! jo kitab tu ney nazil ki main is par eman laya. jo Nabi tu ney bheja main is par eman laayaa.'' to agar us haalat mein usi raat mar gaya to fitrat par marega aur us dua ko sab baton ke akheer mein padh. Bara (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us dua ko dobara padha. jab main (اللهم آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت) par pahuncha to maine ( ورسولك‏ ( (ka lafz ( keh diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi ( yun kaho ( ) ونبيك الذي أرسلت ( .
